high_descs: Turn around and go to the sink, then turn right and go to the counter across from you where the microwave is.
Pick up the knife on the counter, to the right of the spatula.
Cut the tomato, on the counter, in front of the silver canisters into slices.
Move over to your right so that you are in front of the microwave.
Place the knife in the microwave, above the dishwasher.
Move back over to the counter top to your left.
Pick up one of the tomato slices on the back of the counter.
Move back to your right, in front of the microwave.
Place the tomato slice in the microwave, heat it up, and remove the tomato from the microwave.
Turn to your left and go to the sink across from you.
Place the tomato slice on the counter, in front of the sink with the lettuce inside.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife in the microwave and a warm tomato slice on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around, take a right at the sink and walk to the counter.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle to the right of the spatula on the counter.
Slice the tomato on the back area of the counter to the right of the silver bowl.
Turn right and walk to the microwave on the left.
Put the knife inside the microwave and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the counter on the right.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the counter.
Turn right and walk to the microwave on the left.
Put the slice of tomato in the microwave, heat it, remove it and close the door.
Turn left to face the sink.
Put the heated slice of tomato on the edge of the counter in front of the right side of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated slice of tomato on a counter and store a knife in a microwave.

high_descs: Turn left, step forward, turn left and walk to the sink, then make a right to reach the kitchen counter.
Pick up the knife in front of the tomato.
Slice the tomato on the counter.
Turn right and go to the microwave on the left side.
Open the microwave, place the knife inside in between the potatoes, close the door.
Turn left, step forward, then turn right to face the sliced tomato.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Walk to the center of the microwave.
Open the microwave door, place the tomato in front of the knife and turn on. Wait till the microwave is off and remove the tomato.
Turn left to face the kitchen sink.
Place the tomato on the counter space in front of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of tomato on kitchen counter.
